Class DataSetRequest.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jimmoores.quandl.DataSetRequest.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    DataSetRequest

    public static final class DataSetRequest.Builder
extends Object
    Inner builder class. Create an instance using of("QUANDL/CODE"), call any other methods you need, and finish by calling build().
